THIS
IS
MINIBAR.
MiniBar Miami is a hidden cocktail bar in Miami Beach, tucked just off Meridian Avenue inside the Meridian Hotel. Loved by locals and discovered by travelers, we offer strong drinks, curated music, and a laid-back lounge atmosphere that feels like a true neighborhood favorite.
Our space blends the best of South Beach nightlife with a more intimate, elevated experience. Guests come for handcrafted cocktails, daily happy hour specials, and a vibe that’s relaxed, welcoming, and effortlessly cool. Whether you're winding down after the beach or starting your night in the city, MiniBar Miami is where good drinks and good energy come together.
A hidden gem with heart, MiniBar Miami is one of Miami Beach’s best-kept secrets.
